{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f4b70354ae","title":"大字报——“鹦鹉先生”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f429a938a9","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"f4b70354ae"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"a58e8d4c68","name":"赵日月"},{"id":"b9d6e9c96b","name":"北京政法学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3417665dc1","type":"title","text":"大字报——“鹦鹉先生”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"25101b6e14","type":"authors","text":"北京政法学院赵日月","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"f573e46283","type":"paragraph","text":"生理上的变化，超出了科学家的预料，","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"23e7cf896e","type":"paragraph","text":"脚后跟代替了大脑，","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"7036c41c80","type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛的工作由耳朵代劳。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"9c3d990e1f","type":"paragraph","text":"大脑和眼睛跟兰尾肠一样失去了时效，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"00985dbcdb","type":"paragraph","text":"成年光消耗卡热，不起作用的废料，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"44c45ec09c","type":"paragraph","text":"造物主啊！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"a6ab3664b5","type":"paragraph","text":"你应该把这些没有用的器官——眼睛和大脑精简掉，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"8a7db5d123","type":"paragraph","text":"只留下耳朵和咀巴就行了，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"08d9955337","type":"paragraph","text":"耳朵听别人怎样说，咀巴就学着怎样叫。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"627ad9776d","type":"paragraph","text":" 57、5、30、","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"50d26285ac","type":"subtitle","text":"一席对话   　　 赵日月","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"e4eac0d6a7","type":"paragraph","text":"人物：甲(党员)乙(团员)","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"3e99a583ff","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：(对甲)老兄，历次运动中你向来是积极分子，可是这次整风运动怎没见老兄发言呢？","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"7ea8e48814","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：你看，我早就对你说过，你不懂事。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"2049302582","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：我怎么不懂事呢？","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"331b0ceb34","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：过去的运动都是帮领导“正”下面的人，只要你积极，就一定有好处，可以入党，可以升官，这次不同，这次正领导，你要是积极了，运动过后，还有你的好处吗？(扭乙的耳朵，低声说)这是我入党的秘诀。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"0ccea52197","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：(两眼直愕愕的半晌才说)唔！原来如此。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"1637df00b2","type":"paragraph","text":" 注　此文以笔名“明记”在自己论坛发表。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"},{"id":"a863825299","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《北京政法学院右派分子言行汇编》(第3部分)(北京政法学院，1957年10月)。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae"}],"page":{"id":"94028d356e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4b70354ae","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}